Method Detail

addSection

Bus addSection(int secNo,
               Bus bus)
add a bus section object into the busSecList. secNo has to be > 0. There should be no duplication of SecNo. Also, the bus section object, a bus object, is set to inactive.

getSection

Bus getSection(int secNo)
get bus section by secNo. Return null if not found.

isChildSection

boolean isChildSection()
Check if the Bus object is a child bus section object.

splitSection

Bus splitSection(int secNo)
Split the bus section by turning it active. When a bus section is active, it is an independent bus. Otherwise it is part of the parent bus.

connectSection

Bus connectSection(int secNo)
connect a splited bus section by turn it off. A off bus section is a part of the parent bus.

getConnectedBranch

Get the branch object connected to this bus identified by the branch id.
